‚ÄãJetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
‚Äãbe found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
‚Äãand can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
‚Äãoption (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
‚Äã#.idea/
‚ÄãAbstra
‚ÄãAbstra is an AI-powered process automation framework.
‚ÄãIgnore directories containing user credentials, local state, and settings.
‚ÄãLearn more at https://abstra.io/docs
