‚ÄãVisual Studio Code
‚ÄãVisual Studio Code specific template is maintained in a separate VisualStudioCode.gitignore
‚Äãthat can be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/VisualStudioCode.gitignore
‚Äãand can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file. However, if you prefer,
‚Äãyou could uncomment the following to ignore the entire vscode folder
‚Äã.vscode/
